name: Leather & Brass Friendship Bracelet
description:
Beautiful, hand made, leather & brass friendship bracelets with zinc plated hexagon nut fastening. These simple yet stylish bracelets look great layered together or worn on there own.

A variety of colours are available as pictured all of which compliment the brass beading, if you order more than one bracelet you will be sent different colours.

Please contact me for a quote if you would like a custom made bracelet!
